{
  "stem": "19218.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Nobody-- they had no crematoriums in there, but they had a tremendous pit where-- where everybody was thrown in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were in that camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Almost no food at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "What we were doing is working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They called it [GERMAN], you know, it's [GERMAN], which means two mountains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The German industry, towards the end of the war, was going underground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were building factories underneath huge mountains or inside the mountains, so no bomb could penetrate in there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were digging in the tunnels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It took us maybe 10 guys to hold up a drill to drill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was no food given to us at all, just a little hot water or so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were dying just like the flies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And this particular man, David, he was already on his last round really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He couldn't go to work anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They wouldn't even waste a bullet to kill him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because, hey, bullets were hard to come by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they would just let him stay in the barrack and die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They just wouldn't give him anything at all, no piece of bread, no food, nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Well, he was in the barracks for about two days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "That third day, we went to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they chased us out from the tunnel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They said the Americans are nearby someplace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The Russians-- the Americans-- no, it was the Americans, I believe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So they evacuated this camp sometimes in the-- I would say it was April 9, April 10, April 8, of 1945.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So we weren't at that camp long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "First of all, nobody ever survived that camp long, because this was-- because this was the end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, most of the people which-- there was the uprising in Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They were brought to that camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
